        "content": "Web search results for query: \"\"Claude Code\" CLI alternative launched February 2025\"\n\nI'll search for information about \"Claude Code\" CLI alternatives that were launched in February 2025.\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"2025：大语言模型（LLM）之年\",\"url\":\"https://m.36kr.com/p/3640423298125193\"},{\"title\":\"24个关键词！浓缩大模型2025席卷世界这一年\",\"url\":\"http://www.citnews.com.cn/news/212052\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Code 替代品推荐2025:国内可用的5 个AI 终端工具对比 ...\",\"url\":\"https://help.apiyi.com/claude-code-alternatives-china-2025.html\"},{\"title\":\"router-for-me/CLIProxyAPI: Wrap Gemini CLI, Antigravity ...\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/router-for-me/CLIProxyAPI\"},{\"title\":\"Claude code 专区\",\"url\":\"https://waytoagi.feishu.cn/wiki/LJbiwATadi72LUklHpgcexeSnNh?table=tbl2RLq2vzgDkz0u&view=vewye9pPqc\"},{\"title\":\"AI CLI / Plugins / Extension 应用从小白到大师\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnblogs.com/treasury-manager/p/19131789\"},{\"title\":\"24个关键词！浓缩大模型2025席卷世界这一年\",\"url\":\"https://m.sohu.com/a/972634344_117302/?pvid=000115_3w_a\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Code 与其他主流 AI 编程助手工具对比（2025）\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/tomxjc/article/details/149937522\"},{\"title\":\"Claude code 专区\",\"url\":\"https://bytedance.larkoffice.com/wiki/LJbiwATadi72LUklHpgcexeSnNh?table=tblikKoUZJ51bpUz&view=vewzzUnTig\"},{\"title\":\"青蛙小白\",\"url\":\"https://blog.frognew.com/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, I found information about Claude Code and its CLI alternatives that launched in February 2025:\n\n## Claude Code Launch (February 2025)\n\n**Claude Code** was quietly launched by Anthropic in **February 2025** as part of the Claude 3.7 Sonnet announcement. It was introduced as the second item in the announcement without a dedicated blog post.\n\n### Key Details:\n- **Launch Date**: February 2025\n- **Developer**: Anthropic\n- **Type**: Command-line programming agent / CLI tool\n- **Purpose**: An \"agentic coding\" tool that can write code, execute code, check results, and iterate further\n\n## Main CLI Alternatives Launched in 2025\n\nSeveral other major labs launched their own CLI programming agents in 2025:\n\n1. **Codex CLI** (OpenAI) - Launched as \"Codex cloud\" (later renamed \"Codex web\") in early May 2025\n2. **Gemini CLI** (Google) - Called \"Jules\", launched in May 2025\n3. **Qwen Code** (Alibaba)\n4. **Mistral Vibe** (Mistral)\n\n## Third-Party/Independent Alternatives:\n- GitHub Copilot CLI\n- Amp\n- OpenCode\n- OpenHands CLI\n- Pi\n\n## Claude Code Key Features:\n- Deep code awareness through \"agentic search\"\n- Multi-file consistent editing\n- Native terminal & IDE integration (VS Code, JetBrains)\n- Can run Shell/Git/test commands with user authorization\n- Security-focused with confirmation prompts and customizable whitelists\n\nThe search results indicate that 2025 became a significant year for AI-powered CLI programming tools, with multiple major players entering the space following Claude Code's February launch.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
